metadata.name: Flux // Connected
metadata.description:
Companion application showcases all 500 mints from my Art Blocks curated project Flux. All on-chain mints have been collected and connected together as one continuous experience, as well as a mode for viewing out of bounds possibilities via random generation.

Refer to the "external_url" in the token for the IPFS URL for proper native viewing. It is intended for large displays, modern hardware and best viewed in either the Chrome or Safari browsers.

Please contact me if you intend to display this in a public and/or commercial environment.
